  "tutorial header": "ARGUMENTS",
  "tutorial body": "You've started an ARGUMENT. Defeat your opponent by lowering their CONFIDENCE. Picking the correct options will do damage to your opponent. However, picking the wrong options will do damage to <i>your</i> CONFIDENCE. Use context and clues to determine which option to pick."
