  "tutorial header": "DEDUCTIONS",
  "tutorial body": "During investigations, you'll sometimes go over all that you've learned to formulate DEDUCTIONS. Tyrion will think through the case and raise STATEMENTS that must be answered. Use the arrows to construct a sentence that responds to the STATEMENT. While more than one response may be technically true, only one response will be meaningful."
