  "reference name": "Psych",
  "tutorial header": "PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILES",
  "tutorial body": "You'll occasionally need to ARGUE against people and PERSUADE them to cooperate with your investigation. PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILES help you in those ensuing ARGUMENTS. They give you information about your opponent and help you understand which options to pick.\n\n\nYou can fill a person's PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILE by TALKING to them or PRESENTING them certain items."
}

